#Vaccine hesitancy, that is, persons who will probably or definitely not get a #COVID19 vaccine, can be gleaned from the #census household pulse survey. Here, for week #26 (March 3-15, 2021). 

Hesitancy is lowest for seniors age 65+, highest for young adults 25-39. Overall 17.2% https://t.co/SWPKYxktxZ
